  "notes": "The content of this flow will depend on which Agents have changed, and which Agent is the recipient of the information.  The D0148 should be used to update and supersede only that information which the agent needs to know and is currently unaware of.For a definition of the content of the flow in the NHH and HH markets see the scenarios contained in Annex C.Where an AMVLP (Asset Metering Virtual Lead Party) is involved, the MPAN Core must contain an AMSID (Asset Metering System Identifier) and not an MPAN."
